     H            Y.
     F** AM#R02B ********************************************
     F* RETURN #OF BOXES SHORTED IN PACKING
     F*
     F*    LEC.    COPY FROM AM#R02S           2019.03.26
     F*******************************************************
     FAM#PL08 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PNONY   40
     C                     PARM           PDOCK   2
     C                     PARM           PORD#  12
     C                     PARM           PPALT   2
     C                     PARM           PSHID   8
     C                     PARM           PSHIT   6
     C                     PARM           PSURT   9
     C                     PARM           PIAFB   3
     C                     PARM           PIAFP   3
     C                     PARM           PSHORT  30
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     Z-ADD0         PSHORT
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PNONY
     C                     KFLD           PDOCK
     C                     KFLD           PORD#
     C                     KFLD           PPALT
      *
      * get total # of boxes that have been shorted...
      *
     C           KEY       CHAINAM#PL08              50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           R1SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           R1SHME    ANDEQ'SHORT'
     C           R1HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C           R1SHID    ANDEQPSHID
     C           R1SHIT    ANDEQPSHIT
     C           R1SURT    ANDEQPSURT
     C           R12AFB    ANDEQPIAFB
     C           R12AFP    ANDEQPIAFP
     C                     ADD  1         PSHORT            SHORT TOTAL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KEY       READEAM#PL08                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
